document.full_text: u-prince  - michel martelly, a shaven-headed singer and political outsider, won haiti's presidential election in a landslide victory that tapped into deep popular desire for change in the poor, earthquake-battered caribbean state.
document.title: outsider martelly sweeps haiti's presidential election
